
Setup Prerequistites
--------------------

1. Install Raspbian image

2. Install wiringPi library
	sudo apt-get install git-core
	git clone git://git.drogon.net/wiringPi
	cd wiringPi && ./build

3. Test GPIOs
	gpio readall

4. SPI Driver
	sudo raspi-config
	- Advanced options
	- A6 SPI
	- enable interface
	- enable load by default

5. Reboot

